== дёҷз”ігҒ®жңҲ ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|иҫӣ}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|дёҷ}}), the month of {{ill|July|ja|7жңҲ}} is designated as the Heishin month ({{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жңҲ (жҡҰ)}}). However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|з«Ӣз§Ӣ}} until the day before {{ill|White Dew|ja|зҷҪйңІ}}) as applicable.

== дёҷз”ігҒ®ж—Ҙ ==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|йҒёж—Ҙ|1=Senjitsu}} for Heishin is as follows.
=== Selected Day (йҒёж—Ҙ) ===
Heishin day is the 4th day of {{ill|Ten Ten IchijЕҚ|ja|еӨ©дёҖеӨ©дёҠ}}.







