{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Fire Monkey|kanji=дёҷз”і|romaji=hinoe saru|onyomi=heishin|p=bЗҗngshД“n|w=ping-shen|mi=pК°iЕӢВІВ№ КӮЙҷn|y=bing2 san1|j=bing2 san1|ci=pЙӘЕӢ КӮЙҗn|mc=pГҰЕӢ КӮin|oc-bs=praЕӢ КӮin}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}

'''Yang Fire Monkey also known as дёҷз”і''' (hinoesaru (дёҷз”і), heikanosaru (дёҷз”і), heishin (дёҷз”і)) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ}}.

It is the 33rd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ}}, preceded by {{ill|Otsumi|ja|д№ҷжңӘ}} and followed by {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|дёҒй…ү}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢжҖқжғі|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І}} symbol {{ill|Hei|ja|дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|зҒ«}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еҚҒдәҢж”Ҝ}} symbol {{ill|Monkey|ja|з”і}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|йҮ‘}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дә”иЎҢжҖқжғі#зӣёеүӢпјҲгҒқгҒҶгҒ“гҒҸпјү}}) (i.e. Fire overcomes Metal).

== дёҷз”ігҒ®е№ҙ ==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ}} that leaves a remainder of 36 when divided by 60 is a year of Heishin ({{ill|year|ja|е№ҙ}}).
