It is the 33rd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Otsumi|ja|д№ҷжңӘ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|дёҒй…ү|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢжҖқжғі|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Hei|ja|дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|зҒ«|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еҚҒдәҢж”Ҝ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Monkey|ja|з”і|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|йҮ‘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дә”иЎҢжҖқжғі#зӣёеүӢпјҲгҒқгҒҶгҒ“гҒҸпјү|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (i.e. Fire overcomes Metal).

== дёҷз”ігҒ®е№ҙ ==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 36 when divided by 60 is a year of Heishin ({{ill|year|ja|е№ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).
