'''Yang Fire Monkey also known as дёҷз”і''' (hinoesaru (дёҷз”і), heikanosaru (дёҷз”і), heishin (дёҷз”і)) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

It is the 33rd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Otsumi|ja|д№ҷжңӘ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|дёҒй…ү|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢжҖқжғі|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Hei|ja|дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|зҒ«|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еҚҒдәҢж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Monkey|ja|з”і|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|йҮ‘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дә”иЎҢжҖқжғі#зӣёеүӢпјҲгҒқгҒҶгҒ“гҒҸпјү|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) (i.e. Fire overcomes Metal).

