It is the 33rd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Otsumi|ja|1=Yin Wood Goat|2=ja|д№ҷжңӘ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsumi|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|дёҒй…ү|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢжҖқжғі|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Hei|ja|дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|зҒ«|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еҚҒдәҢж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Monkey|ja|з”і|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Monkey|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|йҮ‘|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal|qq=}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дә”иЎҢжҖқжғі#зӣёеүӢпјҲгҒқгҒҶгҒ“гҒҸпјү|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=}}) (i.e. Fire overcomes Metal).

