'''Yang Fire Monkey also known as дёҷз”і''' (hinoesaru (дёҷз”і), heikanosaru (дёҷз”і), heishin (дёҷз”і)) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
It is the 33rd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Otsumi|ja|1=Yin Wood Goat|2=ja|д№ҷжңӘ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsumi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsumi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Goat|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Teiyuu|ja|1=Yin Fire Rooster|2=ja|дёҒй…ү|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Rooster|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢжҖқжғі|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] symbol {{ill|Hei|ja|дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|lt=Hinoe (дёҷ)|2=ja|3=дёҷ|4=zh|5=дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|Fire (зҒ«)|1=Fire (wuxing)|ja|Fire (зҒ«)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|2=uk|3=Р’РҫРіРҫРҪСҢ (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hб»Ҹa (NgЕ© hГ nh)|10=ar|11=Ш§Щ„ЩҶШ§Шұ (ЩҲЩҲ ШҙЩҠЩҶШә)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|2=uk|3=Р’РҫРіРҫРҪСҢ (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hб»Ҹa (NgЕ© hГ nh)|10=ar|11=Ш§Щ„ЩҶШ§Шұ (ЩҲЩҲ ШҙЩҠЩҶШә)|1=Fire (wuxing)|ja|Fire (зҒ«)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|2=uk|3=Р’РҫРіРҫРҪСҢ (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hб»Ҹa (NgЕ© hГ nh)|10=ar|11=Ш§Щ„ЩҶШ§Шұ (ЩҲЩҲ ШҙЩҠЩҶШә)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuel