--> ==Years of Yang Fire Monkey== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 36 when divided by 60 is a year of Heishin ([[:en:Year|year]]). {| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Heishin (дёҷз”ігҒ®е№ҙ)''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 36|36 AD]] * [[:en:AD 96|96 AD]] * [[:en:156|156 AD]] * [[:en:216|216 AD]] * [[:en:276|276 AD]] * [[:en:336|336 AD]] * [[:en:396|396 AD]] * [[:en:456|456 AD]] * [[:en:516|516 AD]] * [[:en:576|576 AD]] * [[:en:636|636 AD]] * [[:en:696|696 AD]] * [[:en:756|756 AD]] * [[:en:816|816 AD]] * [[:en:876|876 AD]] * [[:en:936|936 AD]] * [[:en:996|996 AD]] | * [[:en:1056|1056 AD]] * [[:en:1116|1116 AD]] * [[:en:1176|1176 AD]] * [[:en:1236|1236 AD]] * [[:en:1296|1296 AD]] * [[:en:1356|1356 AD]] * [[:en:1416|1416 AD]] * [[:en:1476|1476 AD]] * [[:en:1536|1536 AD]] * [[:en:1596|1596 AD]] * [[:en:1656|1656 AD]] * [[:en:1716|1716 AD]] * [[:en:1776|1776 AD]] * [[:en:1836|1836 AD]] * [[:en:1896|1896 AD]] * [[:en:1956|1956 AD]] | * [[:en:2016|2016 AD]] * {{ill|2076 AD|ja|2076е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2076|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2076 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2136 AD|ja|2136е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2136|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2136 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2196 AD|ja|2196е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2196|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2196 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2256 AD|ja|2256е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2256|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2256 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2316 AD|ja|2316е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2316|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2316 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2376 AD|ja|2376е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2376|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2376 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2436 AD|ja|2436е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2436|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2436 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2496 AD|ja|2496е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2496|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2496 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2556 AD|ja|2556е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2556|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2556 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2616 AD|ja|2616е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2616|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2616 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2676 AD|ja|2676е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2676|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2676 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2736 AD|ja|2736е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2736|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2736 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2796 AD|ja|2796е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2796|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2796 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2856 AD|ja|2856е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2856|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2856 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2916 AD|ja|2916е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2916|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2916 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2976 AD|ja|2976е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2976|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2976 AD|qq=}} |}
==Months of Yang Fire Monkey== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Sin|ja|иҫӣ|1=Kanoto (иҫӣ)|lt=Kanoto (иҫӣ)|2=ja|3=иҫӣ|4=zh|5=иҫӣ|1=Kanoto (иҫӣ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (иҫӣ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (иҫӣ)|qq=}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|lt=Hinoe (дёҷ)|2=ja|3=дёҷ|4=zh|5=дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:July|July]] is designated as the Heishin month ([[:en:Month|month (calendar)]]). However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from [[:en:Liqiu|Beginning of Autumn]] until the day before [[:en:Bailu (solar term)|White Dew]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yang Fire Monkey== The {{ill|selected day|ja|йҒёж—Ҙ|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for Heishin is as follows. === Selected Day (йҒёж—Ҙ) === Heishin day is the 4th day of {{ill|Ten Ten IchijЕҚ|ja|еӨ©дёҖеӨ©дёҠ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten IchijЕҚ|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten IchijЕҚ|qq=}}.
