q=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2316|comment=changed title based on wikidata|lt=2316 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=24дё–зҙҖ|1=24th century|WD=Q49838}} * {{ill|2376 AD|ja|2376е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2376|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2376 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2436 AD|ja|2436е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2436|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2436 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2496 AD|ja|2496е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2496|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2496 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2556 AD|ja|2556е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2556|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2556 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2616 AD|ja|2616е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2616|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2616 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2676 AD|ja|2676е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2676|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2676 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2736 AD|ja|2736е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2736|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2736 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2796 AD|ja|2796е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2796|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2796 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2856 AD|ja|2856е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2856|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2856 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2916 AD|ja|2916е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2916|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2916 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2976 AD|ja|2976е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2976|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2976 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |}
==Months of Yang Fire Monkey== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Sin|ja|иҫӣ|1=Kanoto (иҫӣ)|lt=Kanoto (иҫӣ)|2=ja|3=иҫӣ|4=zh|5=иҫӣ|1=Kanoto (иҫӣ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (иҫӣ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (иҫӣ)|qq=}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|lt=Hinoe (дёҷ)|2=ja|3=дёҷ|4=zh|5=дёҷ|1=Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дёҷ)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:July|July]] is designated as the Heishin month ([[:en:Month|month (calendar)]]). However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from [[:en:Liqiu|Beginning of Autumn]] until the day before [[:en:Bailu (solar term)|White Dew]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yang Fire Monkey== The {{ill|selected day|ja|йҒёж—Ҙ|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for Heishin is as follows. === Selected Day (йҒёж—Ҙ) === Heishin day is the 4th day of {{ill|Ten Ten IchijЕҚ|ja|еӨ©дёҖеӨ©дёҠ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten IchijЕҚ|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten IchijЕҚ|qq=|ja_comment=еӨ©дёҖзҘһ|1=Tenitsu-shin|2=ja|3=еӨ©дёҖзҘһ|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11442153}}.
