vi|9=Hб»Ҹa (NgЕ© hГ nh)|10=ar|11=Ш§Щ„ЩҶШ§Шұ (ЩҲЩҲ ШҙЩҠЩҶШә)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire (wuxing)|ja|Fire (зҒ«)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|2=uk|3=Р’РҫРіРҫРҪСҢ (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hб»Ҹa (NgЕ© hГ nh)|10=ar|11=Ш§Щ„ЩҶШ§Шұ (ЩҲЩҲ ШҙЩҠЩҶШә)|lt=Fire (зҒ«)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, while the [[:en:Earthly Branches|Earthly Branches]] symbol [[:en:Monkey (zodiac)|Monkey (з”і)]] represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|Metal (йҮ‘)|1=Metal (wuxing)|ja|Metal (йҮ‘)|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (NgЕ© hГ nh)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=РңРөСӮР°Р» (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (NgЕ© hГ nh)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=РңРөСӮР°Р» (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|1=Metal (wuxing)|ja|Metal (йҮ‘)|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (NgЕ© hГ nh)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=РңРөСӮР°Р» (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal (wuxing)|ja|Metal (йҮ‘)|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (NgЕ© hГ nh)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=РңРөСӮР°Р» (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дә”иЎҢжҖқжғі#зӣёеүӢпјҲгҒқгҒҶгҒ“гҒҸпјү|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=|1=Wu Xing|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q218652}}) (i.e. Fire overcomes Metal).
